        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary class="faq-q">Is the discovery call really free?</summary>
          <p class="faq-a">Yes. 30 minutes, no charge, no obligation. I use it to understand where you are and whether I think I can genuinely help. If coaching is not the right next step for you, I will tell you that too.</p>
        </details>
        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary class="faq-q">Do I have to commit to a bundle before the call?</summary>
          <p class="faq-a">No. The discovery call comes first. If we both feel it is a good fit, I will walk you through the options and you can decide from there. No pressure on the call to sign up to anything.</p>
        </details>
        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary class="faq-q">Are sessions online or in person?</summary>
          <p class="faq-a">All sessions are online via video call. This means you can work with me regardless of where in the UK you are based.</p>
        </details>
        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary class="faq-q">What if I am not ready to start a business yet?</summary>
          <p class="faq-a">That is exactly who the Business Plan Bundle is for. You do not need to have launched. You just need an idea you are serious about. The sessions take you from idea to a complete, executable plan.</p>
        </details>
        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary class="faq-q">How is this different from a generic business coach?</summary>
          <p class="faq-a">I have personally started 35 businesses. I am not coaching from a textbook. I am coaching from experience. Every session ends with a written action plan. And I will tell you honestly what I think, even when that is not what you were hoping to hear.</p>
        </details>
        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary class="faq-q">When are sessions available?</summary>
          <p class="faq-a">Sessions run on Wednesdays and Thursdays, 8am to 6pm. You can book your free discovery call directly through Calendly and choose a time that works for you.</p>
        </details>
